author: Pawel_Kaminski_HWS
title: Great little set.
review:
This is the one of my first LEGO Technic sets. I must said,  this is really nicely done set. I love the work of shock absorber piece when I push this F1 to the floor. If you love LEGO like me you should have this F1 :)

P.S. This is my first review on Brickset.com :)
